tip.text: Come here for dinner. Perfect service with a smile on their lips. Almost daily changing menu. Ask for the chefs recommendation. Starters are great as well!
Great food and chilly location. Come here for lunch or a good coffee.
Authentic Japanese restaurant. Really amazing ramen soup. Try the mizo with a green tea. And the service is outstanding.
Unkomplizierte Location. Besitzer ist spitze. Berlin-Hippster-Style
Sehr gute Nudelsuppen. Empfehlenswert. Personal mehr als freundlich.
Most amazing entrecôte in town. Live cooking with perfect wine. Ask for the recommendation of the day.
Great location for a perfect dinner. Come Thursday's for a four course surprise menus (39€). Really good quality and the staff is friendly. Relaxing atmosphere.
Sehr gute Steaks in ordentlicher Größe. NY Strip Medium-Rare ist zu empfehlen sowie der Parmesan-Kartoffel-Stampf.
Had a really nice evening. The owner is nice. Ask for the limoncello for desert. The fish is top.
Not a normal steakhouse. Fancy presentation and good taste. Service could be better. Go for the mixed starter.
Come here for seafood or original Iceland food. Bit overpriced but really good quality. Try the lobster :)
Amazing fresh food. Really nice atmosphere at this place. Check it out. Waiting-time by a gin tonic in the cellar bar.
Just amazing. Don't leave Porto without having dinner here. Friendly staff and best food in town. And really good prices. Loved it.
Really friendly family and a great service. Try the caramelized goat cheese and enjoy a port wine for desert.
Terrific view and nice live music at the evening. Go for a gin tonic and relax.
Perfekter Service und sehr zuvorkommendes Personal. Sehr schöne Wohnungen die der Beschreibung entsprechen.
3 course surprise menu is the standard here. Quality and service are great but the taste was not that special. Bit overpriced.
Great view. Come here for a date and a spectacular scenery.
If you're looking for unusual food and strange meals come here. But there are better places.
